This is our final assignment/submission for "American Military presence in Greenland during the 20th century" constituting Portfolio 5 by mapping the US military presence in Greenland.

NB: The HTML file in this map is simply too big (2,5 Mb) to be presented directly inside the GitHub Repository. For this reason, the HTML file must be downloaded to be viewed and accessed. 
To access the file: Click on the HTML file -> click the top-right download icon, which says "download raw file". Now the file has been downloaded, and our code and findings are presented.
